snippet.title: Wicked Times First Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay Trailer for Wicked Times.
Wicked Times is an rpg manager/autobattler. Slay overgrown creatures sent by the demon Kugraltha. Upgrade your gear. Find new towns and side activities that can help you with gold and experience.

On Itch.io:  https://diamondtao.itch.io/wicked-times
OnSteam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2604240/Wicked_Times/

Diamond Tao: https://diamondtao.com
